{"tid":1508041,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"唔好再推荃灣粒汽油彈","createTime":"2019-08-26T11:43:41.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-26T23:15:06.000Z","uid":9846,"like":267,"dislike":25,"uniUserReply":72,"replies":[{"pid":"362d35ed20c50118fa853dcdc1c8c26223b3bd5d","tid":1508041,"uid":9846,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T11:43:41.000Z","msg":"傻㗎咩，黑暗文宣邊係咁玩，琴日咁撚多直播影住你都想屈狗扔，係咪想比人完美咁反駁先開心，唔好做柒嘢，搞到自己成個林子健咁<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n[已fc] 汽油彈真係由狗度扔 停止抹黑示威者<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1507759\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1507759</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n［炒曬車］汽油彈係由示威者嗰邊掉出嚟<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1507680\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1507680</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n林子健自編自導自演案:<br />\n<a href=\"https://zh.m.wikipedia.org/zh-hk/林子健\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.m.wikipedia.org%2Fzh-hk%2F%E6%9E%97%E5%AD%90%E5%81%A5&d=qutgakuQBXsObMwiKtfrscsFuFiCHHua96MUfZSGoRU%3D&h=fb0218eb\" target=\"_blank\">https://zh.m.wikipedia.org/zh-hk/林子健</a>"},{"pid":"33d808e85c7f70b28c4c094763d4714e4858dc4b","tid":1508041,"uid":33930,"like":21,"dislike":3,"score":18,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T11:44:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4B5ZOzj.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4B5ZOzj.gif&h=0e4bb77e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n九月一號下午一點機場見<br />\n<br />\n901機場和你塞 Channel<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyou\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyou&d=qutgakuQBXsObMwiKtfrscsFuFiCHHua96MUfZSGoRU%3D&h=98b51da6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/stuckwithyou</a><br />\n901機場和你塞 公海<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyouopen\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyouopen&d=qutgakuQBXsObMwiKtfrscsFuFiCHHua96MUfZSGoRU%3D&h=f1b5480a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/stuckwithyouopen</a><br />\n901機場和你塞 宣傳<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyoupromote\